he (1978 film)|Avalanche]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1978\n| ''[[The Bees (film)|The Bees]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1978\n| ''[[Blackout (1978 film)|Blackout]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1978\n| ''[[Deathsport]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1978\n| ''[[The Evil (1978 film)|The Evil]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1978\n| ''[[Jokes My Folks Never Told Me]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1978\n| ''[[Leopard in the Snow]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1978\n| ''[[Outside Chance]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1978\n| ''[[Piranha (1978 film)|Piranha]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[Angels Revenge|Angel's Brigade]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[The Brood]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[Fast Charlie... the Moonbeam Rider]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[The Green Room (film)|The Green Room]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[The Kids Are Alright (film)|The Kids Are Alright]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[The Lady in Red (1979 film)|The Lady in Red]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[Love on the Run (1979 film)|Love on the Run]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[The Prize Fighter]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[Rock 'n' Roll High School]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[Saint Jack]]'' \n|\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[Starcrash]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[Up from the Depths]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1980\n| ''[[Battle Beyond the Stars]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1980\n| ''[[Breaker Morant (film)|Breaker Morant]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1980\n| ''[[The Georgia Peaches]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1980\n| ''[[Humanoids from the Deep]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1980\n| ''[[Mon oncle d'Am\u00e9rique]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1980\n| ''[[The Private Eyes (1980 film)|The Private Eyes]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1980\n| ''[[Shogun Assassin]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1980\n| ''[[Something Waits in the Dark]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1980\n| ''[[The Tin Drum (film)|The Tin Drum]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1981\n| ''[[Firecracker (1981 film)|Firecracker]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1981\n| ''[[Galaxy of Terror]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1981\n| ''[[Mindwarp: An Infinity of Terror]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1981\n| ''[[Quartet (1981 film)|Quartet]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1981\n| ''[[Richard's Things]]'' \n|\n|-\n| 1981\n| ''[[Ruckus (film)|Ruckus]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1981\n| ''[[Smokey Bites the Dust]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1981\n| ''[[Saturday the 14th]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[Android (film)|Android]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[Battletruck]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[The Calling (1982 film)|The Calling]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[Christiane F. \u2013 We Children from Bahnhof Zoo|Christiane F.]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[Fitzcarraldo]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[Forbidden World]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[Galaxy Express 999|Galaxy Express]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[Jimmy the Kid]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[Paradise (1982 film)|Paradise]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[The Personals (1982 film)|The Personals]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[The Slumber Party Massacre]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[Sorceress (1982 film)|Sorceress]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[Tag: The Assassination Game]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[Three Brothers (1982 film)|Three Brothers]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1982\n| ''[[Time Walker]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1983\n| ''[[Deathstalker (film)|Deathstalker]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1983\n| ''[[Last Plane Out]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1983\n| ''[[Screwballs]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1983\n| ''[[Space Raiders (film)|Space Raiders]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1984\n| ''[[Love Letters (1984 film)|Love Letters]]''\n|\n|-\n| 1984\n| ''[[Suburbia (film)|Suburbia]]'' \n|\n|-\n| 1984\n| ''[[The Warrior and the Sorceress]]''\n|\n|}\n\n===New regime===\nMost of these films are currently owned by Vine Alternative Investments.\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Release date\n! Title\n! Notes\n|-\n| January 13, 1984\n| ''[[Angel (1984 film)|Angel]]''\n|\n|-\n| March 9, 1984\n| ''[[Children of the Corn (1984 film)|Children of the Corn]]''\n|\n|-\n| March 11, 1984\n| ''[[Nausica\u00e4 of the Valley of the Wind (film)|Warriors of the Wind]]'' (P/U)\n| 1984 recut of ''[[Nausica\u00e4 of the Valley of the Wind (film)|Nausica\u00e4 of the Valley of the Wind]]''; ''Nausica\u00e4'' director [[Hayao Miyazaki]]'s distaste of the recut is said to have led to [[Studio Ghibli]]'s stringent \"no cuts\" policy for international distribution of their works.\n|-\n| April 28, 1984\n| ''[[The Initiation (film)|The Initiation]]''\n|\n|-\n| August 3, 1984\n| ''[[The Philadelphia Experi